      "rationale": "Validation specimens are production-identical to the device under assessment. ASTM F1717 UHMWPE block represents low-density osteoporotic bone, constituting the worst-case clinical scenario. Loading modality (compression-bending) replicates the dominant in vivo load mode. Validation activity relevance to COU confirmed at required level."
